{
  "title": "矩阵乘法证明",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div class=\"asset-content entry-content\" id=\"main-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; letter-spacing: -0.12px; line-height: 21.6px; widows: 1; word-spacing: 2.4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">大多数人在高中，或者大学低年级，都上过一门课《线性代数》。这门课其实是教矩阵。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/3BFACF9E891A82CD6942CDDEC60E528F.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">刚学的时候，还蛮简单的，矩阵加法就是相同位置的数字加一下。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/2B2E1A543BBC6B96936DB9C7A64E8E6E.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">矩阵减法也类似。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">矩阵乘以一个常数，就是所有位置都乘以这个数。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/460C2FC4C331640DD8B5DBB1338E7E5F.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">但是，等到矩阵乘以矩阵的时候，一切就不一样了。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/091E945BAA3D785D2F3F24011C99B316.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">这个结果是怎么算出来的？</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">教科书告诉你，计算规则是，第一个矩阵第一行的每个数字（2和1），各自乘以第二个矩阵第一列对应位置的数字（1和1），然后将乘积相加（ 2 x 1 + 1 x 1），得到结果矩阵左上角的那个值3。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/67D0CAE11FD639F2CF3FB0823F86341A.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">也就是说，结果矩阵第m行与第n列交叉位置的那个值，等于第一个矩阵第m行与第二个矩阵第n列，对应位置的每个值的乘积之和。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">怎么会有这么奇怪的规则？</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">我一直没理解这个规则的含义，导致《线性代数》这门课就没学懂。研究生时发现，线性代数是向量计算的基础，很多重要的数学模型都要用到向量计算，所以我做不了复杂模型。这一直让我有点伤心。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">前些日子，受到<a href=\"https://nolaymanleftbehind.wordpress.com/2011/07/10/linear-algebra-what-matrices-actually-are/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none;\">一篇文章</a>的启发，我终于想通了，矩阵乘法到底是什么东西。关键就是一句话，矩阵的本质就是线性方程式，两者是一一对应关系。如果从线性方程式的角度，理解矩阵乘法就毫无难度。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">下面是一组线性方程式。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/C8B63FD21608357FB2505DB32DFB73A4.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">矩阵的最初目的，只是为线性方程组提供一个简写形式。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/5AC2DF801DC62CA780007635D4ED2722.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">老实说，从上面这种写法，已经能看出矩阵乘法的规则了：系数矩阵第一行的2和1，各自与 x 和 y 的乘积之和，等于3。不过，这不算严格的证明，只是线性方程式转为矩阵的书写规则。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">下面才是严格的证明。有三组未知数 x、y 和 t，其中 x 和 y 的关系如下。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/AC3EDF98450532923F40540792C3C677.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">x 和 t 的关系如下。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/A92CE8E674621B74995889B932D39FD9.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">有了这两组方程式，就可以求 y 和 t 的关系。从矩阵来看，很显然，只要把第二个矩阵代入第一个矩阵即可。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/ACBECA48394C1E86ABB7CECF07070FFC.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">从方程式来看，也可以把第二个方程组代入第一个方程组。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/F6892773E77DA2FA177EFBF108564F75.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">上面的方程组可以整理成下面的形式。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/E3C08F693409720F13298D97C15333E9.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">最后那个矩阵等式，与前面的矩阵等式一对照，就会得到下面的关系。</font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/7E02C2854FDECEDC6A80A75506CD5695.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0.3em solid rgb(224, 223, 204); border-top-left-radius: 1em; border-top-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-right-radius: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em;\"></font></p><p style=\"margin: 1em 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: none; line-height: 28.8px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Georgia\">矩阵乘法的计算规则，从而得到证明。</font></p></div>"
    }
  ]
}